{"tid":2030010,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"互動故《我是外星人，準備侵略地球》","createTime":"2020-05-22T13:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T13:28:28.000Z","uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b06722a87a5dcb3c6b87eae09691ebd4b86aca3","tid":2030010,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:47:07.000Z","msg":"故事開始：<br />\n<br />\n          地球讀者好，我來自遙遠的摩囉星，作為一個地道兼出色的的外星人，幾乎無所不能，近日，小弟無所事事，係乘坐太空巴士閒遊途中，發現一顆蔚藍的星球，經大腦分析，原來這顆星球俗稱「地球」。<br />\n<br />\n     根據黑暗森林法則，小弟唔客氣了，準備來一場大屠殺。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n   首先，請選擇我降落地區<br />\n<br />\nA：印度<br />\nB：美利堅合眾國<br />\nC：中華人民共和國<br />\nD：日不落帝國"},{"pid":"2702549b96d885718b2d6edc795a520c6c11e5a2","tid":2030010,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"率先到3次，為選項結果"},{"pid":"4a7a5b35345b7896377697573547fa6e90947b97","tid":2030010,"uid":306052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:19:47.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"1c23ed0ffbc6a8db8d5b76757e9457464ac75fa5","tid":2030010,"uid":306052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:20:08.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"953e4af8ee233fae6486081c66a33671b8f31921","tid":2030010,"uid":306052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:20:22.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"09d7b07cb422954aa3e5f0952a4bf006dbf5890d","tid":2030010,"uid":170723,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T14:49:38.000Z","msg":"c"},{"pid":"c7c68d3850c28a9944903b519094ac298ba151c2","tid":2030010,"uid":307228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T13:28:28.000Z","msg":"C"}],"pinned":{"pid":"2702549b96d885718b2d6edc795a520c6c11e5a2","tid":2030010,"uid":191300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T13:48:00.000Z","msg":"率先到3次，為選項結果"}}